               <head>De simplicibus medicinae ('Circa instans'), etc.; 15th century</head>
               <msContents>
                  <msItem n="1" xml:id="MS_e_Mus_122-item1">
                     <author key="person_14780021">Matthaeus Platearius (?)</author>
                     <title key="work_3133">De simplicibus medicinae</title>
                     <rubric>Tractatus de simplicibus medicinis, auctore Johanne Mateario medico Salernitano</rubric>
                     <note>Known as 'Circa instans', because the pref. beg. 'Circa instans negotium in simplicibus medicinis': here without title or author's name. The work is arranged alphabetically, beginning with 'Aloen': on fol. '379' is added the latter part (Y-Z) of a similar treatise.</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="la">Latin</textLang>
                  </msItem>
