                     <title key="work_16311">Antidotarium</title>
                     <rubric>Tractatus de unguentis &amp; pillulis</rubric>
                     <incipit>Pomum ambre diminutum sic fit</incipit>
                     <incipit>Pillule ante cibum peroptime</incipit>
                     <note>Cf. <bibl type="repertory"><ref target="https://cctr1.umkc.edu/find/$db=eTK&amp;ms=1057D">eTK 1057D</ref></bibl> ('Pomum ambre est duplicatum'), 1049C (?)</note>
